org.robolectric.res.builder

Class XmlFileBuilder.XmlResourceParserImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.robolectric.res.builder.XmlFileBuilder.XmlResourceParserImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.res.XmlResourceParser, android.util.AttributeSet, org.xmlpull.v1.XmlPullParser
    Enclosing class:
    XmlFileBuilder

    public static class XmlFileBuilder.XmlResourceParserImpl
extends Object
implements android.content.res.XmlResourceParser
    Concrete implementation of the XmlResourceParser.

    Clients expects a pull parser while the resource loader initialise this object with a Document. This implementation navigates the dom and emulates a pull parser by raising all the opportune events.

    Note that the original android implementation is based on a set of native methods calls. Here those methods are re-implemented in java when possible.

    See Also:
    https://github.com/android/platform_frameworks_base/blob/master/core/java/android/content/res/XmlBlock.java
